data.description: Home Sweet Home!  Beautiful 3-bedroom, 2 1/2 Bathroom home that offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and style. NEW ROOF (2023)!  Chef ready Kitchen with NEW Granite Countertops, Breakfast Bar, NEW Stainless Appliances, Stylish Cabinetry, and Breakfast Nook with Bay Windows. Welcoming Living Room with Gas Log Fireplace.  NEW Beautiful Hardwoods and Carpet downstairs. 1st Floor Primary Bedroom with Walk-In Closet and Desirable Master Bath ready for relaxation. Two more Generously Sized Bedrooms upstairs sharing a Tastefully Appointed Full Bathroom. Step Out Back onto your own private deck. Don't miss Your chance to make this House Your Home! Call Today for YOUR Private Showing!
